Hints for #ruby, IRC:
*_methods returns an array of symbols, not an array of strings, str[nr] returns an "char" and no number,  same for ?char, case when allows now when val : func  anymore there is ; better.  Strings and other like Regex, Match Data, and Symbol have now encodings and Iconv was removed, String is not an Enumerable anymore, and for 2.0 lines and each_line react different,
